fects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/158386/', '', 'Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Tryptophan, Vilazodone', '', 1767369485);
